<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.11">
<l>uṟaṅkuvāṉ pōlyōku ceyta perumāṉai</l>
<l>ciṟantapoḻil cūḻkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉco</l>
<l>ṉiniṟaṅkiḷarnta vantāti yāyirattu ḷippattā</l>
<l>liṟantupōy vaikuntañ cērāvā ṟeṅṅaṉēyō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Going beyond</l>
<l>by these ten among the Antāti thousand, resplendent with [sound] colours,</l> 
<l>composed by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr surrounded by superior groves,</l>
<l>on the great lord who did Yoga like someone slumbering,</l>
<l>how [could that] not be the way to join Vaikuntam?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
